&lt;li&gt;Score and rank prospective partners against clear commercial criteria — overlapping customer base, co-sell motion, deal size influence, and pipeline/revenue potential — rather than technical novelty alone.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Say no to partnerships that lack a credible path to revenue, even when they are technically compelling, and be able to articulate why.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
